Option 2 â€” Wrap MJPEG in an HTML page

Create a simple HTML page (e.g., /var/lib/openhab/html/cam.html):

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="margin:0">
  <img src="http://192.168.0.7:8081/?action=stream" style="width:100%; height:100%;">
</body>
</html>


Serve it via OpenHAB (or any local HTTP server) and point your oh-webframe-card to it:

- component: oh-webframe-card
  config:
    url: "http://192.168.0.7:8080/cam.html"
    height: 300px
    width: 100%
    title: "Laptop Camera"


page => new layout => grid => add widget => configure
